OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Water cremation is set to be made      
OL,6, available for the first time in the UK.
OL,8,FThe process, known as resomation, uses 
OL,9,Fa mix of potassium hydroxide and water 
OL,10,Fto break down human remains in what is 
OL,11,Fbilled as a more sustainable option.   
OL,13,FIt takes four hours - the bones remain,
OL,14,Fand are powdered then returned to loved
OL,15,Fones in a similar way to ashes, in an  
OL,16,Furn.                                   
OL,18,FResomation is used in Canada, South    
OL,19,FAfrica and many US states.             
